- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with neural networks and their application to natural language processing tasks. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the use of transfer learning techniques for improving the performance of sentence encoders, which could be applied to image-related tasks as well. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with neural networks and their application to natural language processing tasks.
